#: ../../peps/peps/pep-0558.rst:619
msgid ""
"any call to ``PyFrame_GetLocals()``, ``PyFrame_GetLocalsCopy()``, "
"``_PyFrame_BorrowLocals()``, ``PyFrame_FastToLocals()``, or "
"``PyFrame_FastToLocalsWithError()`` for the frame"
