#: ../../peps/peps/pep-0558.rst:650
msgid ""
"``PyFrame_GetLocals(frame)`` is the underlying API for ``PyLocals_Get()``."
msgstr ""

#: ../../peps/peps/pep-0558.rst:652
msgid ""
"``PyFrame_GetLocalsCopy(frame)`` is the underlying API for "
